### 2.4 Protect Sensitive Data (IMPORTANT!)
```bash
# Check for sensitive data before committing
grep -r "SECRET_KEY" . --include="*.py" --include="*.env"
grep -r "PASSWORD" . --include="*.py" --include="*.env"
grep -r "API_KEY" . --include="*.py" --include="*.env"

# Move sensitive data to environment variables if not already
# settings.py should look like:
# import os
# from dotenv import load_dotenv
# load_dotenv()
# SECRET_KEY = os.getenv('SECRET_KEY')